data.description: This amazing home shows like new. This was the model home of Tyside II with all the upgrades.  Espresso stained cabinets, panty and island. Formal Dining w/ coffered ceiling or flex space. Hardwood floors on main level, gas logs fireplace and loft on second floor. Laundry in second floor for added convenience.
